; Dungeon Demo — level 1, dynamic layer (everything that changes during play).
; One record per line:
;
;   <kind> <type> <x> <z> [facing] [key=value ...]
;
; Kinds: monster, item, button (decorations are static — they go in the
; .map file). type is a catalog id (catalog/monsters.cat for monsters). x/z
; are grid cells of level1.map, (0,0) top-left, x grows east, z grows south.
; facing is north/east/south/west (default south); buttons must face a solid
; wall. Examples of upcoming kinds:
;   item torch 4 1
;   button lever 9 5 east target=door_a
;
; Monsters sprinkled one or two per room across the level.
; Flee demo (docs/ai.md P2): a skittish critter facing the party in the start
; room; it perceives them at once and runs (fleebelow>1 = flees on sight).
monster skel_coward 6 3 west
; Skirmisher demo (docs/ai.md P1c): stands down the open corridor east of the
; start room so the party rounds the corner into it; it kites away and shoots.
monster skel_archer 10 4 west
; Caster demo (docs/ai.md P2): further down the same corridor; kites and hurls
; firebolts (spell=firebolt) through the shared engine.
monster skel_mage 16 4 west
; Lurker demo (docs/ai.md P2): dormant in the pillared hall until the party comes
; within ~2 cells, then springs and pursues relentlessly.
monster skel_lurker 14 6 north
; Swarm demo (docs/ai.md P2): a small cluster (medium size packs several per cell)
; that surrounds; senses omnidirectionally.
monster skel_swarm 13 7 north
monster skel_swarm 14 7 north
monster skel_swarm 13 8 north
monster skel_human 6 6 north
monster skeleton 15 7 west
monster blob 27 4
monster mummy 4 12 east
monster skeleton 6 15 north
monster skeleton 12 14 east
monster blob 17 16
monster mummy 27 13 west
monster blob 5 22
monster skeleton 8 28 north
monster mummy 3 25 east
monster skeleton 19 27 north
monster mummy 17 24
monster blob 27 27

; Rune items — step onto one to add its symbol to the party satchel, then
; memorize it onto a character from the sheet. A few near the start to find.
item rune_fire 4 4
item rune_air 5 4
item rune_water 6 4
item rune_earth 7 4

; The fab.com weapon models, lined up just ahead of the spawn — now pickable
; weapons (they share these cells with the runes above; each takes its own
; quarter). viking_dagger=dagger, plus khukri/snake_dagger/french_dagger.
item dagger 3 4
item khukri 4 4
item snake_dagger 5 4
item french_dagger 6 4

; Non-rune items (placeholder visuals) — a sampler near the start for testing
; pickup / carry load / hand commands.
item dagger 4 5
item leather_armor 5 5
item tunic 6 5
item apple 7 5
item bread 8 4
; Container packs — pick up and drop onto a pack slot in the sheet to equip.
item ammo_pouch 2 5
item medicine_pouch 3 5
; A restricted pack (herb pouch: ingredients only) + ingredients to test it.
item herb_pouch 2 4
item herb 3 4
item mushroom 9 4
